What is the purpose of anything, really? It all comes back to that mystical &quot;Why?&quot;. I choose to kill and destroy for my own personal empowerment. As you bear the title of Wizard, you do the same, unless you claim to be First Circle in your studies.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Pure Hatred is as simplistic a creed as you can follow. Furthermore, it is devoid of any redeeming spiritual qualities. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
